  "prompt": "Can people see if you have viewed their instagram?",
  "response": "No, generally other users cannot see if you have viewed their Instagram profile. Instagram does not provide a feature that notifies users about who has visited or viewed their profile. However, this changes for certain types of content: Instagram Stories and Instagram Live videos. Users can see who has viewed their Stories and Live videos for a limited time. For regular posts, profile visits, or browsing the feed, there is no way for users to know who has viewed them.",
